{"tid":835031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇人生改造課程","createTime":"2018-09-24T14:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T15:28:08.000Z","uid":205492,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3d766534ebdeee6de6b29ca02a74fda93f01a5a1","tid":835031,"uid":205492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:29:52.000Z","msg":"事源是咁的有一個識左好耐既朋友<br />\n同我講人生改造課程 佢話好實用 <br />\n一定會學到好多野 不斷係咁好評呢個課程<br />\n佢聲稱上緊第3階段既課程<br />\n然而我上網見到一啲討論區話<br />\n呢個係一種洗腦同催眠你既垃圾課程<br />\n其後更提及到3階課程既Leader<br />\n需要令到一定數量既人參加<br />\n否則會被組織既人責罰<br />\n當日佢係咁同我講呢個課程好有用<br />\n從而慫恿我去參加 呢個課程需要大量既金錢<br />\n所以我唔排除可能比佢利用<br />\n希望大家可以比啲關於人生改造課程既睇法我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6fac86eb5584665eb41bbce039402e943c56f9","tid":835031,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:30:34.000Z","msg":"弱智"},{"pid":"7e810a5057bfc82ae4234e7ee1cd84d1e7ce63d3","tid":835031,"uid":149324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:30:53.000Z","msg":"真係好有用 我成為左人類第一位變革者"},{"pid":"0ce5d14f3b8491ffe2db24a2cb03db197f0baf44","tid":835031,"uid":205645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:31:44.000Z","msg":"you will become another person"},{"pid":"c931617b1ee524aae168b0caf5503018825deb8e","tid":835031,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T14:36:05.000Z","msg":"好有用<br />\n可以狂揸女同學對波"},{"pid":"c6868100a38247052283375223f2d56a5ecb7487","tid":835031,"uid":202412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T15:28:08.000Z","msg":"人生改造<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}